        "created_at": "2017-07-24T00:13:04.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Pity about the Tempier.</p>\n<p>There is a lot of fun to be had with 1981 Bordeaux. I just bought an '81 Conseillante for less than a bottle of the '13 (truly abysmal vintage) would cost me. Very much looking forward to it.</p>\n<p>Angludet is a real '81 sleeper if you ever see it.</p>",
